==English==
===Noun===
'''turbulence'''

# Irregular motion of air.
# quick, [[irregular]] [[movement]] caused by similar movement in the surrounding air or water

# Annoying halfpipe shaped wind on Sonic Riders that allows you to catch up to rivals by increasing your top speed.  It also gets in the way when you don't want it to.  It has advantages and disadvantages at times.

